<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="straight-adj">straight <strong><em>adj</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /streɪt/    美 /streɪt/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>(笔) 直的；平直的；</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a straight road / line
直路/直线</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>整齐的；端正的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I have straight white teeth.
我的牙齿整齐洁白。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Is my tie straight?
我的领带正不正？</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.<strong>正直的；诚实的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>He is a straight judge.
他是位正直的法官。</p></div>

<h4 id="4">4.<strong>纯粹的：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We are always in need of straight humor articles.
我们一直都需要纯粹的幽默文章。</p><footer>2011 北京</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="earn-get-straight-as">earn / get straight A’s</h3>
<p>1.<strong>得全优成绩</strong>  </p>
<h3 id="get-sth-straight">get sth straight</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[口语] 弄清楚某事</strong>  </p>
<h2 id="_3">派生词汇</h2>
<p>straighten /'streɪtn/ vt   </p></div>